channel.title: We Need an Official Discord Community Page!
channel.description: Hey guys, it has recently come to my attention that there is no official Auxy community page on Discord! I think it would be great if one was created by a developer or someone else of a higher status in the Auxy community, such as @Auxy, @Fredrik, or even @iammane. Tell me what you guys think about potentially creating an official Auxy page on Discord. Thanks! (Also I put this as #random category, feel free to correct me on that)
